text: Schranz is a German surname. Notable people with the surname include: *Andreas Schranz (born 1979), Austrian football goalkeeper *Ivan Schranz (born 1993), Slovak football player *Karl Schranz (born 1938), Austrian alpine skier *Károly Schranz (born 1952), Hungarian violinist *Wolfgang Schranz (born 1976), Austrian tennis player ==See also== * Schranz, a musical genre (see: Hardtechno) Category:German-language surnames
